# Orquestrador dnd-api

Docs: [`docs/infrastructure.md`](../../docs/infrastructure.md) · [`docs/architecture.md`](../../docs/architecture.md)

Genérico: shared-ai (`nestjs`, `typeorm`, `jest`, `testing`, `sql`, `postgres`, `supabase`, `vercel`, `rest-api`).

## Skills locais

| Quando | Skill |
|--------|-------|
| Glossário / slugs PT-EN | `dnd-glossary-pt` |
| Tabelas, FKs, views PHB | `rpg-catalog-model` |
| Queries prontas nas views | `phb-query-views` |
| `db:setup` / migrate / seed | `postgres-apply-catalog` |

## Rules locais

`architecture` · `api-contract` · `phb-data`

## Ops rápidos

- TypeORM: `schema: 'rpg'`, `synchronize: false`; pooler **6543** em prod
- JWT: `jsonwebtoken` + JWKS — sem `jose` no runtime
- Testes: `*.queries.spec.ts` / `*.application.spec.ts` / e2e; `npm run test:cov`
- Migrations: não editar aplicadas; seeds FK-safe; `dev-reset` só em dev
